oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: First Annual Gospel Quartet Union Live Concert
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Split fountain printing; Gospel music; Concerts;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (black on split fountain red to green) announcing the first annual Gospel Union Live Concert featuring the Dixie Travelers, The New Traveling Stars, Songs of Grace, The Spiritual Messengers, Gospelettes, Shouting John and the New Spiritual Key, and the True Spirit Gospel Singers at Shiloh Interdenomination Church on October 20 and 21.
